  "detailed_description": "Block Tower TD 2 is a strategic game in the roguelike style with original innovations. Build worlds from blocks, choose random upgrades, each game will be unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the World!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/79e73823678b59467208ea3a2b125ba3.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=550 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/79e73823678b59467208ea3a2b125ba3.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/79e73823678b59467208ea3a2b125ba3.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unleash your potential in creating defensive strategies, playing in a world where every block is important for your defense. Create unique tactics by placing blocks in the right places.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the Towers</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/fcf1aee68addefac60604c3e671e92fd.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=550 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/fcf1aee68addefac60604c3e671e92fd.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/fcf1aee68addefac60604c3e671e92fd.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Tower placement is a key aspect in Tower Defense games. Especially in Block Tower: build them on elevations, leave space for resources, cleverly combine blocks. Each tower has an experience bar: the earlier it is built, the stronger it becomes at the end of the game. Skilful tower placement will make your defense stronger and more efficient.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Upgrades</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/76e2fecacc565abebac41646737a4e68.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=584 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/76e2fecacc565abebac41646737a4e68.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/76e2fecacc565abebac41646737a4e68.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The sequence of upgrades plays a crucial role in progressing through each stage. Optimize your strategy based on resources, magical towers, or fortified defense. The random block generation, combined with tactical decisions, gives the game almost endless replayability.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harvest Resources</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/317682f747dc6c7725a21f7e1300b33e.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=550 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/317682f747dc6c7725a21f7e1300b33e.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/317682f747dc6c7725a21f7e1300b33e.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Develop your economic strategy wisely. Early investment in economic buildings can be risky but will provide a significant advantage in the end. The random distribution of resources in each game creates new strategic challenges, requiring your creative approach and decision-making skill.",
  "about_the_game": "Block Tower TD 2 is a strategic game in the roguelike style with original innovations. Build worlds from blocks, choose random upgrades, each game will be unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the World!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/79e73823678b59467208ea3a2b125ba3.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=550 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/79e73823678b59467208ea3a2b125ba3.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/79e73823678b59467208ea3a2b125ba3.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unleash your potential in creating defensive strategies, playing in a world where every block is important for your defense. Create unique tactics by placing blocks in the right places.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the Towers</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/fcf1aee68addefac60604c3e671e92fd.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=550 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/fcf1aee68addefac60604c3e671e92fd.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/fcf1aee68addefac60604c3e671e92fd.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Tower placement is a key aspect in Tower Defense games. Especially in Block Tower: build them on elevations, leave space for resources, cleverly combine blocks. Each tower has an experience bar: the earlier it is built, the stronger it becomes at the end of the game. Skilful tower placement will make your defense stronger and more efficient.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Upgrades</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/76e2fecacc565abebac41646737a4e68.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=584 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/76e2fecacc565abebac41646737a4e68.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/76e2fecacc565abebac41646737a4e68.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The sequence of upgrades plays a crucial role in progressing through each stage. Optimize your strategy based on resources, magical towers, or fortified defense. The random block generation, combined with tactical decisions, gives the game almost endless replayability.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harvest Resources</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/317682f747dc6c7725a21f7e1300b33e.poster.avif?t=1721411082\" width=550 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/317682f747dc6c7725a21f7e1300b33e.webm?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837350/extras/317682f747dc6c7725a21f7e1300b33e.mp4?t=1721411082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Develop your economic strategy wisely. Early investment in economic buildings can be risky but will provide a significant advantage in the end. The random distribution of resources in each game creates new strategic challenges, requiring your creative approach and decision-making skill.",
